lead_paragraph: If Matt Moore's performance in Hollywood was an audition, the Tampa Bay left-hander definitely helped his chances to get the part with the Los Angeles Dodgers.

headline.print_headline: Moore Pitches Rays to Their 1st Win at Dodger Stadium, 3-1
